1. *Inspektor* je bio zadužen za istragu. (The inspector was responsible for the investigation.)
2. On je naredio *inspektoru* da čini svoj posao. (He ordered the inspector to do his job.)
3. *Inspektori* su otišli u potragu za osumnjičenim. (The inspectors went searching for the suspect.)
4. Oni su odlučili da pošalju *inspektora* da proveri. (They decided to send an inspector to check.)
5. Oni su zatražili da *inspektori* daju izveštaj. (They requested the inspectors to give a report.)